about.summary: Diff, patch and merge for data frames. Document changes in data sets and use them to apply patches. Changes to data can be made visible by using render_diff. The V8 package is used to wrap the 'daff.js' JavaScript library which is included in the package.

name: r-daff
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '0.3.5' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-daff
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/daff_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/daff/daff_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: d2ebc6c9ad891c5956593099d799c20dda9fc00ea76c9f6a1ff7d412846bec03

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 2
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-v8 >=0.6
    - r-jsonlite
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-v8 >=0.6
    - r-jsonlite

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('daff')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('daff')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: http://github.com/edwindj/daff
  license: MIT
  summary: Diff, patch and merge for data frames. Document changes in data sets and use them
    to apply patches. Changes to data can be made visible by using render_diff. The
    V8 package is used to wrap the 'daff.js' JavaScript library which is included in
    the package.
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - xhochy
